Load the simulated nutrition dataset from this package

Source: R/data_io.R, R/datasets.R
load_simulated_nutrition_data.Rd

The full simulated nutrition dataset used in the tutorial is shipped as an RDS under inst/extdata/ (to avoid loading it automatically).

Loads the file inst/extdata/simulated_nutrition_data.rds.

Usage

load_simulated_nutrition_data()

load_simulated_nutrition_data()

Value

An object read by readRDS().

The R object stored in simulated_nutrition_data.rds.

Examples

nut <- load_simulated_nutrition_data()
str(nut)
